## Project: Osusu Sales Agent Management System
- Started: 2026-05-19 01:59:05 UTC
- GitHub token provided for repo creation
- Repository created: https://github.com/Airpyk-98/Osusu-Sales-Agent-Management-System
- Description: Premium 2D customer management system for sales agents with roles SUPER_ADMIN, TEAM_LEAD, TEAM_MEMBER.
- Brand colors: Purple and white, logo from getosusu.com
- Key features:
   * Team management (Super Admin creates teams, onboards/approves team members, assigns/unassigns team lead)
   * Team Lead can onboard team members (pending Super Admin approval)
   * Team Members add customers to their register
   * Each customer has an order book where orders can be created, edited, deleted
   * Order statuses: delivered, pending, cancelled, returned (can be updated in batch for entire list or selected orders)
- Add-ons considered:
   * Analytics dashboard (sales performance, team performance)
   * Export/import (CSV, Excel) for customers and orders
   * Notification system (email/SMS for order status changes, approvals)
   * Audit log (track all changes for compliance)
   * Multi-language support (i18n)
   * Dark/Light mode toggle
   * Role-based access control (RBAC) fine-grained permissions
   * Data backup and restore
   * API rate limiting and security headers
   * CI/CD pipeline with automated testing
- Tech Stack:
   * Frontend: React 18 with Redux Toolkit, Tailwind CSS, React Router v6
   * Backend: Node.js (Express) with PostgreSQL, Sequelize ORM
   * Real-time: Socket.io for live order updates
   * DevOps: Docker, Docker-compose, GitHub Actions
   * Testing: Jest, React Testing Library, Supertest
   * Documentation: Swagger/OpenAPI
- Current status: Repository initialized, about to create initial project structure and planning documents.

